{"word":"H8104 - שָׁמַר - shâmar - shaw-mar' - Beward","slug":"H8104","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁמַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shâmar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shaw-mar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Beward"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DE;&#x05E8; - sha&#x0302;mar</b> - <i>shaw-mar'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>hedge</i> about (as with thorns), that is, <i>guard</i>; generally to <i>protect</i>, <i>attend to</i>, etc.: - beware, be circumspect, take heed (to self), keep (-er, self), mark, look narrowly, observe, preserve, regard, reserve, save (self), sure, (that lay) wait (for), watch (-man)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3461\">H3461</a>, <a href=\"#/H4929\">H4929</a>, <a href=\"#/H4931\">H4931</a>, <a href=\"#/H7763\">H7763</a>, <a href=\"#/H8106\">H8106</a>, <a href=\"#/H8107\">H8107</a>, <a href=\"#/H8108\">H8108</a>, <a href=\"#/H8109\">H8109</a>, <a href=\"#/H8110\">H8110</a>, <a href=\"#/H8111\">H8111</a>, <a href=\"#/H8112\">H8112</a>, <a href=\"#/H8113\">H8113</a>, <a href=\"#/H8114\">H8114</a>, <a href=\"#/H8116\">H8116</a>, <a href=\"#/H8117\">H8117</a>, <a href=\"#/H8118\">H8118</a>, <a href=\"#/H8119\">H8119</a>, <a href=\"#/H821\">H821</a>"}]}